# Development environment

## Testing

- `@web/test-runner` with **Playwright** (Chromium, Firefox, WebKit)
- **WebKit does not work** on Ubuntu 24.04 (ICU `uidna_nameToUnicode_70` mismatch) — use Chromium (optionally Firefox)
- Single package: `npm run test --workspace=<name>` or `cd packages/<name> && npx web-test-runner --playwright --browsers chromium`

## Install

`PUPPETEER_SKIP_DOWNLOAD=1` during `npm install` avoids a long Puppeteer browser download (`render-fidelity-tools`). Cached browsers: `~/.cache/puppeteer/`.

## Pre-commit

Husky hook (`scripts/pre-commit.sh`) auto-formats staged `.ts` with `clang-format`. Husky v7 may need `npx husky install` once.

